research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Deer Park, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The City Council consists of seven elected members: a Mayor and six Council Members. Information on specific council positions for all members was not uniformly available across all sources, so general 'Council Member' is used where a specific position was not stated. The official website lists the Mayor and three Council Members with their positions. The Texas Municipal League directory provided the names of the remaining Council Members.
